								</svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Aprendizaje Federado</h3>
							<p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Dispositivos wearables, LLMs y sistemas distribuidos</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="research-card group">
							<div class="w-10 sm:w-12 h-10 sm:h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3 sm:mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
